data.title: Feted By Joe Rogan, Collabing With Snoop Dogg: Meet Yonatan Dor, The Viral AI Filmmaker Who Has Hollywood In His Sights
data.description: AI filmmaker Yonatan Dor, co-founder of The Dor Brothers, is targeting Hollywood after his viral videos were endorsed by Joe Rogan and Snoop Dogg.
data.author: Jake Kanter
